1106
01:25:43,000 --> 01:25:46,000
 Pa, konzumiram i dalje dosta.

1107
01:25:46,000 --> 01:25:50,000
 Nemam, mislim, u biti ja konzumiram...

1108
01:25:50,000 --> 01:25:54,000
 Konzumiram, to je isto pokovareni način.

